			<h2>About Us</h2>
			<p>Allerton Investments operate exclusively in the specialist supported living sector. We work alongside our partners to achieve the best result possible with the needs of each service user always at the forefront of our mind. Our partners are Local Authorities, care operators, Clinical Commissioning Groups, housing associations and charitable organisations.</p>
			<p>Our core focus is on the individual and their needs allowing them the ability to lead a more independent lifestyle. Due to the increase in demand and a lack of availability of specialist housing, those who require care and support to lead independent lives are prevented from doing so. This may lead to individuals being placed into housing that is not suitable for their needs.</p>
