				<p>Allerton Group focuses on the importance of giving back in activities, in particular operating with behaviours that benefit our global community simultaneously with our passion for real estate focused charities; and young upcoming entrepreneurs. Allerton Group recognises its responsibility to respect the environment and is committed to ensuring that all procedures are operated whilst ensuring the reduction of environmental impact that business activities may have, alongside optimising the use of regulations concerning the environment.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6 order-md-2 col-lg-3">
