			<div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6 order-md-1 col-lg-9">
				<p>We continuously seek in new innovative ways to reduce energy consumption; wastage of raw materials and production; and harmful emissions that may occur as a result of our activities to operate Allerton Group. The community as a whole has a duty of care when the environment is concerned, and we are aware that it is important for Allerton Group to hold the intention of reducing utility consumption and the production of waste, by ensuring that our management and staff are aware of their individual responsibilities and to enforce these intentions through good housekeeping practices.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
